<!:TITLE=Close Workbench><l:helppage><l:helphead>Close Workbench<l:/helphead>
<l:helpbody>
This feature is only available for AMIGA users!

If you use Close Workbench you will not be able to enter the Workbench and run other programs at the same time as Fields of Battle. You can use Close Workbench if you want to save memory, thereby running Fields of Battle more smoothly.
